      },
      "date": "2019-06-26 15:19:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nIndeed, I did not include any test parameter to run sanity-krb5 because Maloo does not have a proper Kerberos environment.\n\nI have a containerized KDC that could be dynamically instantiated for that purpose, but there is still the Kerberos principals handling that would need to be fully automated (generate them, then install them on the corresponding nodes). This is certainly possible to make that happen, but that will require some work with the test infrastructure.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
